title: THE RED TEN 004 (2013) (ComixTribe) (Digital) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
And then there were seven...

How far does the killer's reach extend? After leaving the rest of the team behind on the island, one more "hero" finds out in gruesome fashion.

The Red Ten is a ten-issue superhero retelling of Agatha Christie's classic novel, "And Then There Were None."

RATING: Teen + Up
FORMAT: 32 pages, color (#3 of 10 maxi-series)

SCRIPT: Tyler James
ART: Cesar Feliciano
INKS: Vic Moya
COLORS: Gus Ucha
LETTERS: Tyler James
COVER: Charles Paul Wilson III
EDITORS: Steve Colle & Steven Forbes

PUBLISHER: ComixTribe
